{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"9f22503b-4166-5e5d-bcfd-b536663a3e80","html":"<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c0beee94f486e52cc59694703de4991f/f570d/telegram-botfather.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"flavor wheel\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c0beee94f486e52cc59694703de4991f/f570d/telegram-botfather.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c0beee94f486e52cc59694703de4991f/c5a17/telegram-botfather.png 512w,\n/static/c0beee94f486e52cc59694703de4991f/f570d/telegram-botfather.png 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2>The Challenge</h2>\n<p>This is a project born from an internal idea, a lot of times was asked us to develop solutions to manage auctions. There are a lot of auctions applications, typically web based, but we wanted to do something innovative, exploiting the power of Telegram, a platform that we appreciate a lot.</p>\n<h2>The Solution</h2>\n<p>We developed this telegram bot as a platform to serve both users, willing to publish auctions than users that want to bid for items.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7120e3b296012043d689a558d386ad77/7e261/astone-telegram-bot.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 409px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 88.75305623471883%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Astone\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7120e3b296012043d689a558d386ad77/7e261/astone-telegram-bot.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7120e3b296012043d689a558d386ad77/7e261/astone-telegram-bot.png 409w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 409px) 100vw, 409px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>With <a href=\"https://telegram.me/AstoneBot\">Astone</a> user can create an auction from Telegram itsef, is in place an approval process to avoid publishing contents that can infringe copyright or other rules.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0f5d950724f98862f3ba4d2ebc3d288f/7e261/astone-auction.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 409px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 97.06601466992664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Astone Auction\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0f5d950724f98862f3ba4d2ebc3d288f/7e261/astone-auction.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0f5d950724f98862f3ba4d2ebc3d288f/7e261/astone-auction.png 409w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 409px) 100vw, 409px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>When an auction is approved, a start date and time is set. When auction starts, Astone creates an engagement experience, with the pressure given by the same experience a user can live going to a real auction.</p>\n<h2>Â The outcome</h2>\n<p>The outcome is a proof of concept that is used as starting point for a lot of custom projects. Occasionally the original bot is updated bringing to it some improvements.</p>\n<p>The original project is released as open source <a href=\"https://github.com/guglielmino/astone-bot\">here</a></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"July 17, 2018","title":"Astone, the Telegram auctions bot","description":"Astone, reltime auction platform for Telegram","tags":["Telegram","MongoDB","Node.js","Bot"]}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"9f22503b-4166-5e5d-bcfd-b536663a3e80"}}